text: The 2016 The Hague Open was a professional tennis tournament played on clay courts. It was the 24th edition of the tournament and was part of the 2016 ATP Challenger Tour. It took place in Scheveningen, Netherlands between 25 and 31 July 2016. ==Singles main draw entrants== ===Seeds=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! width="70"| Country ! width="175"| Player !
